Currently seeding from 1 location.
Looking to get a few more up in the next few hours.

Hum, well, I'm not sure what happened, but mediainfo is reporting this as stereo now.
It plays and sounds fine, but it's not 5.1

I don't understand how that happened, because when I did the final muxing with TSMuxer, it recognized the file as AC3 5.1

I will do more experimenting with S16E02

Upon further review, I have found that all previous 720p releases were 192kbps AC3 audio, just as these files are in this torrent.
Even the commerically available BluRays are the same audio format.

So, I was trippin' for nothing - all is well.  
Enjoy.
